ad.title: Nanny/Babysitter with years of full-time experience
ad.content:
Hello! My name is Amelie, I am 22 years old and I have over 5 years of nannying and babysitting as well as tutoring experience. 
From 2022 to 2024, I lived in Boston and San Francisco, USA and worked for three families as a live-in nanny/Au Pair. Having lived, worked and studied in the US, I am fluent in English, but my native language is German! 
The children that I used to take care of were between 5 and 15 years old. I also have lots of experience with twins. Furthermore, I was a babysitter for many families during my time in the US and before - I took care of babies as young as 10 days old and provided over night newborn care, practiced language skills with toddlers and helped school-aged kids with their homework. 
I am also very experienced with private tutoring - since 6 years, I offer tutoring for students from grade 1 to 10 in the subjects German, English, maths and other subjects on request. 
I love pets and also love to help take care of them! 
Currently I'm a student at the University of Luxembourg working on getting my Bachelor's degree in Psychology. 
I would be happy to hear from you! 

Kind regards, liebe Grüße, chaleureusement, 
Amelie
